Method Detail

getTotalCount

public java.lang.Integer getTotalCount()

Returns the total count as specified by the Brightcove Media API.

This will only be accurate if the Videos object is created via the JSON constructor, and the option to report total count is enabled in the call to the Media API.

Returns:
Total count of all videos - note that this may be different than Videos.size() if there are more than 100 videos in the Media API response
